Package: ComptoxR
Title: Wrappers and Functions for Accessing USEPA CompTox Chemical
    Dashboard and Other Products
Version: 1.2.2.9003
Authors@R: 
    person("Sean", "Thimons",
    email = "thimons.sean@epa.gov",
    role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
Description: ComptoxR is designed to leverage the USEPA CCTE's APIs for
    accessing the underlying data that makes up the CompTox Chemical
    Dashboard. It includes functions to access or recreate data from the
    Dashboard and Cheminformatics products to inform rapid chemical
    risk screening. A method of weighing and prioritizing a group of
    chemical is also included.
License: `use_mit_license()`, `use_gpl3_license()`
